code: public static Bucket createBucket(final Storage storage, final String bucketName) {     return new Bucket(storage, (BucketInfo.BuilderImpl) BucketInfo.newBuilder(bucketName)). }

public static Blob createBlob(final Storage storage, final String bucketName, final String blobName, final long blobSize) {     return new Blob(storage, (BlobInfo.BuilderImpl) BlobInfo.newBuilder(bucketName, blobName).setSize(blobSize)). }
